.le;14-May-1992 - Module IFFNTF
.list
.le;^*I2NTF\*#-#The /DENSITY qualifier is now permitted the value of 6250 bpi.
.le;^*I2NTF\*#-#A bug has been fixed so that the fixed attributes, FC and OR are
